---
/**
 * HERO SECTION COMPONENT
 * 
 * Purpose: Main landing section introducing the humanitarian organization "De Gaza al Mundo"
 * Position: First section of the homepage, sets tone and call-to-action
 * 
 * Key Features:
 * - Two-column responsive layout (text + hero image)
 * - Mission statement with badge, title, and detailed description
 * - Four key objectives displayed in icon grid
 * - Primary CTA button (Telegram group join)
 * - Styled hero image with Palestinian flag color accents
 * 
 * Layout Strategy:
 * - Mobile: Single column, image on top (reversed flex order)
 * - Desktop: Two columns side-by-side (text left, image right)
 * - Image sized smaller for better balance (max-w-xs mobile, sm tablets)
 * 
 * Design Philosophy:
 * - Trust building through transparency badge
 * - Emotional connection via hero image
 * - Clear value proposition with 4 objectives
 * - Single, focused call-to-action
 */

// === IMAGE IMPORTS ===
// Hero image showing resilience and hope
